import React from 'react'

import { AppIconContainer } from './AppIconContainer'
import { THEME } from '../../../theme'


export const AppBonusIcon = ({ color = THEME.MAIN_COLOR }) => (
  <AppIconContainer
    width="21"
    height="15"
    viewBoxWidth="21"
    viewBoxHeight="15"
  >
    <rect x="1" y="1" width="19" height="13" rx="2" stroke="#3C3E3F" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"/>
    <path d="M1 6H20" stroke="#3C3E3F" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"/>
  </AppIconContainer>
)
